This paper is about integrating machine learning into database management systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of cs.DB (Databases). The paper specifically focuses on using deep learning techniques for feature engineering, which is a topic that falls under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
